== 光驱 ==

PlayStation 3的光盘驱动器是一个多合一光驱，支持多种不同的格式。

=== BD ===

[[Blu-ray|Blu-ray]] 光驱为2倍速, [[区域限制|区域编码]] 类型 allowing the use of:
* [[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]] BD-ROM<ref name="PS3 support manual">{{Cite web |url=http://www.playstation.com/manual/pdf/PS3-01-1.6_1.pdf |title=PlayStation 3 "Safety & Support" manual |accessdate=2010-01-22 |archive-date=2008-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080216091247/http://www.playstation.com/manual/pdf/PS3-01-1.6_1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> ([[DVD区码|DVD区域匹配]], 即1区，2区 等等, and All)
* [[Blu-ray|BD-ROM]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" /> ([[Blu-ray#Region_codes|BD region matched]], i.e. Area A, Area B, etc., and All)
* [[BD-R|BD-R]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" />
* [[BD-RE|BD-RE]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" /> (not compatible with BD-RE version 1.0)

=== DVD ===

[[DVD|DVD]]光驱为8倍速, region coded type allowing the use of:
* [[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]] DVD-ROM<ref name="PS3 support manual" /> (PlayStation 区域匹配,  [[NTSC-J|NTSC-J]], [[NTSC制式|NTSC-U/C]], [[PAL制式|PAL]] or [[NTSC-C|NTSC-C]])
* [[DVD-ROM|DVD-ROM]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" />
* [[DVD-Video|DVD-Video]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" /> ([[DVD区码|DVD区域匹配]], 即1区，2区 等等., and All)
* [[DVD-Audio|DVD-Audio]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" /> (仅DVD视频内容)
* [[DVD+R|DVD+R]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" />
* [[DVD+RW|DVD+RW]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" />
* [[DVD-R|DVD-R]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" />
* [[DVD-RW|DVD-RW]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" />
* [[AVCHD|AVCHD]]<ref name="PS3 support manual" />
* [[Direct_Stream_Digital|DSD Disc]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.playstation.com/manual/pdf/PS3-11-1.8_1.pdf |title=PlayStation 3 80GB model for Mexico "Safety & Support" manual |accessdate=2010-01-22 |archive-date=2011-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715093812/http://www.playstation.com/manual/pdf/PS3-11-1.8_1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
